    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund increased policing against homophobic hate crimes",
        "additional_details": "We are in 2022 and it\u2019s time we take steps forwards and not backwards!\r\n \r\nOn halloween I was involved in a homophobic hate crime attack and I now want the Government to do more to prevent homophobic hate crimes. Stand with us and help continue the fight to protect LGBTQ+ rights. We need more funding for increased policing to protect our streets and keep people safe, and take action against those who commit these crimes.",
        "background": "We want the Government to do more against homophobic hate crimes, by funding increased policing to tackle these crimes. It\u2019s time we all stood together to help prevent people being attacked and abused just for being themselves.",
